-O-Sitam]]''|| Guy who teased 'Meena'\n|-\n|''[[Bandhan (1998 film)|Bandhan]]''|| Police Inspector\n|-\n|''[[Pardesi Babu]]''|| Nandu\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 1999 ||''[[Sikandar Sadak Ka]]''|| Bunty Chawla\n|-\n|''[[Haseena Maan Jaayegi]]''|| Pritam Nath\n|-\n|''[[Pyaar Koi Khel Nahin]]''||\n|-\n|''Jaalsaaz''|| Ranjit Rai\n|- \n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2000 ||  ''Daak Bangla''||\n|-\n|''[[Kunwara]]''|| Ajay\n|-\n|''[[Deewane]]''|| Vishal's cousin\n|-\n|''[[Karobaar: The Business of Love]]''|| Ramlal's son\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2001 ||''Master''|| Kailash 'K. C.' Chaudhry\n|-\n|''[[Inteqam]]''|| Rocky\n|-\n|''Hum Deewane Pyar Ke''|| Tony\n|-\n|''[[Jodi No. 1]]''|| Vikramjit R. Singh\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" | 2002 ||''[[Maine Dil Tujhko Diya]]''|| Raman Chopra\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2004 ||''[[I - Proud To Be An Indian]]''|| I's brother\n|-\n|''[[Dil Ne Jise Apna Kaha]]''|| R. Tripathi\n|-\n| 2005 ||''[[Paheli]]''|| Ghost\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2007 ||''[[Shaadi Karke Phas Gaya Yaar]]''|| Bunty\n|-\n|''[[Nehlle Pe Dehlla]]''|| Hansa\n|-\n|''[[Bombay to Goa (2007 film)|Journey Bombay to Goa: Laughter Unlimited]]''|| Dr. Kushal Bhardwaj\n|-\n|''Sajna Ve Sajna''|| Jibran\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2008 ||''[[Mehbooba (2008 film)|Mehbooba]]''|| Shravan's friend\n|-\n|''[[Tandoori Love]]''|| Superstar Ramesh\n|-\n|''Phir Ayegi Woh Raat''||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2010 ||''[[Benny and Babloo]]''|| Negi\n|-\n|''[[The Desire (2010 film)|The Desire: A Journey of a Woman]]''|| \n|-\n| ''Khallballi: Fun Unlimited''||\n|-\n| 2011 ||''Faraar - On The Run''|| Wilson D'Souza\n|-\n| 2014 ||''[[Ekkees Toppon Ki Salaami]]''|| Arnab Sharma\n|-\n| 2016 ||''[[Aman Ke Farishtey]]''||Vikram\n|-\n| 2019 ||''[[Bharat (film)|Bharat]]''|| Hariwant Mehra \"Babli\"\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Series !! Role !! Notes\n|-\n| 1984\u201385 || ''[[Hum Log (TV series)|Hum Log]]'' || Prince Ajay Singh ||\n|-\n| 1993 || ''[[Zee Horror Show]]'' || Raj || Segment: Khauff\n|-\n| 1994\u20